----
> **[[span class="ruby"]]永[[span class="rt"]]なが[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]井[[span class="rt"]]い[[/span]][[/span]] [[span class="ruby"]]悠[[span class="rt"]]ゆう[[/span]][[/span]]研究員補佐**
