[[tab 「裏切者の」]]
= [[[debugger|]]]
----
> **[[span class="ruby"]]花[[span class="rt"]]はな[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]筐[[span class="rt"]]がたみ[[/span]][[/span]] [[span class="ruby"]]並[[span class="rt"]]ならべ[[/span]][[/span]]諜報員**
> [[size 0%]]　[[/size]]
