> **[[span class="ruby"]]雲[[span class="rt"]]くも[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]手[[span class="rt"]]で[[/span]][[/span]] [[span class="ruby"]]典[[span class="rt"]]のり[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]三[[span class="rt"]]み[[/span]][[/span]]運転手**
